job.title: Indian Navy Sailor Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 350 vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:350

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Sailor for Matric Recruit (MR) – Oct 2021 batch 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for 10th pass has been published by the Indian Navy for Sailor vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Sailor, from

19-07-2021, and till 23-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Sailor in the Indian Navy, your 10th class must be completed from a recognized Board

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 19-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 23-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

Indian Navy Sailor Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Indian Navy Sailor Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Sailor. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of the Indian Navy and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by the Indian Navy 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
